vvv  Additional document of [yamahei/rubycast](https://github.com/yamahei/rubycast) vvv

I add a command "googlehome.rb" to julbouln/rubycast.
This command can let GoogleHome - on the same LAN - speak.
and this can search GoogleHome by name.

$ ruby -I lib bin/googlehome.rb --text="こんにちは" --name="ファミリー ルーム"

See the whole options with
$ ruby -I lib bin/googlehome.rb -h
